data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home in Buda's tranquil Sunfield neighborhood, where contemporary design meets classic comfort. The exterior's pleasing aesthetics hint at the attention to detail found within.    Step inside to a radiant living area where natural light dances across an open floor plan, highlighting a kitchen epitome of modern sophistication. A central island, accented with granite countertops, invites interaction, while the stainless steel appliances stand ready for culinary adventures. Upgraded details like tasteful curtains add elegance, and practical additions such as full gutters ensure the home’s maintenance is as effortless as its style.    The second floor is a realm of relaxation, featuring an expansive game room and built-in desks that create a perfect blend of leisure and utility. The luxurious owner's suite offers a private sanctuary with its generous walk-in closet and sumptuous en-suite.    The home’s versatility is evident in the first-floor study, discreetly designed with a closet to double as a guest room, complete with access to a well-appointed guest bath.    Outside, the backyard's expansive deck emerges as a crowning feature, marrying functionality with visual appeal. It's a versatile space that extends the home’s warmth to the outdoors, ideal for lively entertainment and serene solitude.    With overhead storage in the garage, every inch of the home is optimized for ease and enjoyment. This isn't just a residence—it's a canvas for living well, where every upgrade, from the full gutters to the built-in amenities, enhances the tapestry of home life. This is where memories will be made, moments cherished, and tranquility embraced. $5k Seller Credit!
